 This install applies to "Pirates/Pirates Gold CD남"  1987-1993 Microprose.

 This install requires WHDLoad to be in the path. It can be found in the
 WHDLoad package.

 It can be quit by pressing num '*' (key can be changed with Tooltype "QuitKey=").

 * ECS version *

 The installed program requires 0.5 MB ChipMem and 1.0 MB OtherMem.

 The game requires an installed A500 Kickstart 1.3 image.
 The kickstart image must be located in the directory "Devs:Kickstarts" and
 must be named "kick34005.A500". The image can be extracted from a A500 with
 tools like 'GrabKick' or similar which can be found on aminet.
 If the image is of wrong version or altered in any way WHDLoad will quit with
 an appropriate requester.
 Additionally the file "kick34005.A500.RTB" must be installed in the same
 directory as the kickstart image. It can be found in the archive 
 "util/boot/skick346.lha" on aminet.

 * CD남/unofficial AGA version *

 The installed program requires 1.0 MB ChipMem and 2.0 MB OtherMem.

 The game requires an installed A1200 or A4000 Kickstart 3.1 image.
 The kickstart image must be located in the directory "Devs:Kickstarts" and
 must be named "kick40068.A1200" (resp kick40068.A4000). 
 The image can be extracted from a A1200 (resp A4000) with tools like 'GrabKick'
 or similar which can be found on aminet.
 If the image is of wrong version or altered in any way WHDLoad will quit with
 an appropriate requester.
 Additionally the file "kick40068.A1200.RTB" (resp "kick40068.A4000.RTB")
 must be installed in the same directory as the kickstart image.
 It can be found in the archive "util/boot/skick346.lha" on aminet.

 If you have problems with this installation please try and get a newer
 version of this package from the WHDLoad WWW-Page. If that doesn't help try
 some Tooltypes like NOCACHE, NOAUTOVEC, NOVBRMOVE, NOMMU, PAL or NTSC. If
 that also fails, please inform the author via the Bug-Report-Form which
 can be accessed on the WHDLoad WWW-Page or create a mantis issue directly
 at http://mantis.whdload.de

 For the full WHDLoad package, other installs and updates refer to:
	http://www.whdload.de/
 or	aminet:dev/misc/whdload#?
 and	aminet:game/patch/

 version 1.5 (19.05.2024)
 - install script rewritten & enhanced
 - CD32 version updated for better saved games
 - ECS version memory upgraded
 - added glowicon

 version 1.4 (30.11.2004)
 - rewritten installs for WHDLoad v16
 - unofficial AGA version (actually floppified CD남 version) support
 - reworked install script & readme
 - fixed access fault while quitting game in ECS version

 version 1.3 (2003)
 - Kixx floppy version supported
 - for floppy version, CUSTOM tooltype allows to select a savegame at startup
 - source code included

 version 1.2 (2003)
 - floppy version supported
 - manual protection removed (floppy, thanks LockPick)
 - instructions included

 version 1.1 (2003)
 - really supports original CD남 version, and german support
 - install script only installs required files, and not the huge anims
 - runs german executable if language is set to german in the workbench

 version 1.0 (xx.xx.2002) done by JOTD:
 - initial release, CD남 only
 - access fault fixed
 - source code included
 - joypad emulated with function keys

   F5 = blue button
   F6 = green button
   F7 = yellow button
   F8 = pause
   F9 = control menu, allows to save

 notes:

 This install was the result of a big cooperation with all the patchers:

- Wepl for writing Kickstart 1.3 patcher
- Psygore for real joypad button support in lowlevel library
- Harry for nonvolatile library emulation
- JOTD for specific Pirates! patches, KickCD32, lowlevel lib emulation,
  and Kickstart 3.1 patcher.
- Bored Seal for providing real ISO image.
